This paper discusses the integration of femtocells with macrocells in cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses call admission control and traffic modeling, which are topics related to information theory and systems and control theory, respectively. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also likely categories. The paper also mentions the improvement of performance, which is a topic related to multimedia and human-computer interaction, leading to cs.MM (Multimedia) as another possible category. Finally, the paper discusses the importance of handling handover calls, which is a topic related to cryptography and security, leading to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as a less likely category.
